title: Caution sign beside draft pick???

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: Why is there a Red Caution Sign next to normal Draft pick??

replies.body: Nothing shows when you hover over it? It could be a warning for long queue times or something of the like, I am unsure. I don't see it on my client.
Nothing happens when i hover over it no
Do you own the 16 champions you need? Can you select the queue at all?
yes i do own almost every champ and yes
If you can queue as normal I'd say it's probably just a visual bug and I'd recommend you try running a **client repair** through settings (the gear icon top right) > Initiate Full Repair.
